title: Do Cambridge Uni Students Know Everything? | StreetSmart
description: In this video, Max Fosh goes around the streets of Cambridge University asking students trivia questions to test their knowledge.
summary: Max Fosh quizzes Cambridge University students on various trivia questions to see how much they know.
payoff: The payoff comes when the students struggle to answer some basic questions, showcasing that even students at a prestigious university like Cambridge don't know everything.
